= Pages Only Page 1 =

This page is part of the pages only pack, which contains no external dependencies. It serves as a foundation that other packs depend on.

== Overview ==

Pages only page 1 is a standalone component that provides core functionality. It is referenced by multiple other packs including the [[dependent pack]] and [[multi dependency pack]].

== Dependencies ==

This page has no dependencies and is referenced by:
* [[alpha page]] - part of the dependent pack
* [[beta page]] - part of the multi dependency pack

== Related Content ==

See also [[pages only page 2]] which is part of the same pack. Together, these pages form the complete pages only pack that other systems depend on.

== Implementation Details ==

This page contains implementation details that are essential for the proper functioning of dependent systems. When this pack is imported, users can rename these pages while maintaining the dependency relationships.
